	(text "Dual Core ESP32-S3 240Mhz \n1.91\" AMOLED 240×536\n512KB SRAM and 384KB ROM, \n16MB Flash and 8MB PSRAM\nQMI8658 6-axis IMU\nmicroSD card reader\noptional touch screen option\nESP32-S3-AMOLED-1.91-M\n\nSome pins are broken out on\nunderneath PCB via pinsockets\n\nUltra-low-profile USB-C cables\nrouted underneath the PCB to \npower/program each ESP32"
